#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""HTTP task-map service for Kigo remote map generation.

Kigo posts the active task's extreme points plus its requested bbox.  The
service first tries a ready standard 3-arcsecond XCM cache whose map still
leaves the route at least 20 km from the edge, then crops a POL_HighRes-style
base XCM and injects runway rectangles.  If no base XCM covers the request, it
falls back to a standard mapgen request.
"""

